@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
[*] --> AppLoading
AppLoading --> MapReady : node dataset loaded
AppLoading --> FatalError : dataset invalid

MapReady --> CategoryFocused : category selected
CategoryFocused --> NodeFocused : node selected
NodeFocused --> NodeFocused : related node selected
NodeFocused --> CategoryFocused : zoom out
NodeFocused --> HistoryReview : history item selected
HistoryReview --> NodeFocused : restore focus
CategoryFocused --> MapReady : reset view
NodeFocused --> MapReady : reset view

MapReady --> ReducedMotionMode : prefers-reduced-motion
ReducedMotionMode --> MapReady : preference disabled

FatalError --> AppLoading : retry
@enduml
